String get kBody => """
<p>Angel Di Maria showed his worth as he set up the first and scored the winner to give Paris St Germain a 2-1 win against champions Lille in Ligue 1 after Lionel Messi limped off injured.</p>
<p>The home side - without Kylian Mbappe through illness - fell behind when Ligue 1's top scorer Jonathan David netted his eighth of the campaign with 31 minutes on the clock.</p>
<div class="sdc-site-outbrain sdc-site-outbrain--AR_5" aria-hidden="true" data-component-name="sdc-site-outbrain" data-target="" data-widget-mapping="" data-installation-keys="" data-init="true">
<div id="outbrain_widget_0" class="OUTBRAIN" data-src="https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/12454403/lionel-messi-injured-but-angel-di-maria-stars-as-paris-saint-germain-beat-lille-european-round-up" data-ob-template="365MediaGroup" data-widget-placement="" data-widget-id="AR_5" data-is-secured="true" data-consent-string="" data-consent-version="2" data-ob-mark="true" data-browser="chrome" data-os="macintel" data-dynload="" data-idx="0">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
<p>Lionel Messi, a doubt before the match with a muscular problem, was then withdrawn at the interval.</p>
<div class="sdc-article-widget sdc-site-oddschecker" data-component-name="sdc-site-oddschecker">
<div class="ocw QXJ0aWNsZSBQcm9tbw==" data-oc-no="1">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
