</ul>
<div class="sdc-article-widget sdc-article-image">
<figure class="sdc-article-image__figure">
<div class="sdc-article-image__wrapper" data-aspect-ratio="16/9"><img class="sdc-article-image__item" src="https://e0.365dm.com/21/10/768x432/skysports-angel-di-maria-psg_5564318.jpg?20211029215839" sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw" srcset="https://e0.365dm.com/21/10/384x216/skysports-angel-di-maria-psg_5564318.jpg?20211029215839 380w, https://e0.365dm.com/21/10/768x432/skysports-angel-di-maria-psg_5564318.jpg?20211029215839 760w, https://e0.365dm.com/21/10/1600x900/skysports-angel-di-maria-psg_5564318.jpg?20211029215839 1024w, https://e0.365dm.com/21/10/2048x1152/skysports-angel-di-maria-psg_5564318.jpg?20211029215839 2048w" alt="Angel Di Maria scored late on to see PSG past Lille " /></div>
<figcaption class="sdc-article-image__caption"><span class="sdc-article-image__visually-hidden">Image:</span><span class="sdc-article-image__caption-text">Angel Di Maria scored late on to see PSG past Lille</span></figcaption>
</figure>
</div>
<p>But Marquinhos converted Di Maria's cross after 74 minutes before the Argentine stole the three points following a neat one-two with Neymar with just two minutes remaining.</p>
<p>PSG extend their lead over Lens at the summit of Ligue 1 to 10 points. Lille, who would have deserved better after a convincing first half, are 11th with 15 points.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div class="sdc-article-widget sdc-article-image">
<figure class="sdc-article-image__figure">
<div class="sdc-article-image__wrapper" data-aspect-ratio="16/9"><img class="sdc-article-image__item" src="https://e0.365dm.com/21/10/768x432/skysports-psg-marquinhos-lille_5564319.jpg?20211029215931" sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw" srcset="https://e0.365dm.com/21/10/384x216/skysports-psg-marquinhos-lille_5564319.jpg?20211029215931 380w, https://e0.365dm.com/21/10/768x432/skysports-psg-marquinhos-lille_5564319.jpg?20211029215931 760w, https://e0.365dm.com/21/10/1600x900/skysports-psg-marquinhos-lille_5564319.jpg?20211029215931 1024w, https://e0.365dm.com/21/10/2048x1152/skysports-psg-marquinhos-lille_5564319.jpg?20211029215931 2048w" alt="Marquinhos scored the equaliser for PSG" /></div>
<figcaption class="sdc-article-image__caption"><span class="sdc-article-image__visually-hidden">Image:</span><span class="sdc-article-image__caption-text">Marquinhos scored the equaliser for PSG</span></figcaption>
</figure>
</div>
<h3>Bundesliga - Hoffenheim see off Hertha</h3>
<p><strong>Hoffenheim</strong>&nbsp;scored twice with Andrej Kramaric and Sebastian Rudy in the first half to beat 10-man&nbsp;<strong>Hertha Berlin</strong>&nbsp;2-0 and snap their three-game winning run in all competitions.</p>
<div class="ad ad--teads">
<div class="sdc-site-au " data-ad-format="teads" data-type="" aria-hidden="true">
<div id="in-article-desktop" class="sdc-site-au__teads" data-role="ad-container" data-config="{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;in-article-desktop&quot;,&quot;ad-type&quot;:&quot;teads&quot;,&quot;targeting&quot;:[],&quot;size&quot;:{&quot;mobile&quot;:[[4,4]],&quot;tablet&quot;:[[4,4]],&quot;desktop&quot;:[[4,4]]}}" data-targeting="{&quot;platform&quot;:&quot;live&quot;,&quot;strnativekey&quot;:&quot;eY5NpN2YvRtG5PACRZHya5vd&quot;,&quot;videoStrnativekey&quot;:&quot;NBWeknhck8efFVVz4HuiDqND&quot;,&quot;amp-advert-targeting&quot;:{&quot;platform&quot;:&quot;live&quot;},&quot;advert-targeting&quot;:{&quot;platform&quot;:&quot;live&quot;},&quot;artId&quot;:&quot;12454403&quot;}" data-targeting-strnativekey="" data-targeting-platform="" data-tag="20346936/skysports/football/news" data-component-name="sdc-site-mpu" data-peer39-url="https://tags.peer39.com/1497/trg_1497.js" data-peer39-id="1497" data-peer39-timeout="2500" aria-label="Advertisement" data-tolerance="2" data-init="true">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="standard_11" class="st-placement standard_11 inArticle">
<div class="st-adunit st-reset st-show">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
<p>The Berliners went into the game with two consecutive league wins that had lifted them off the bottom of the table and victory in the German Cup second round in midweek.</p>
<div class="sdc-article-widget sdc-article-related-stories" data-component-name="sdc-article-related-stories">
<div class="sdc-article-related-stories__content">
